        <abstract> 
<p>Has made observations on pollination mechanism in <hi rend="italic">Medicago sativa</hi> [<hi rend="italic">J. Linn. Soc. Lond. (Bot.)</hi> 9 (1867): 327–9], which his brother-in-law [J. D. Hooker] would accept. Wants to check that CD has not already made them.</p>  
<p>Also sends interpretation of <hi rend="italic">Salvia</hi>.</p>  
<p>His observations come from following CD’s generalisation in <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> [p. 79] on necessity of out-crossing.</p> 
        </abstract>
